report_errors.name: Yuvraj Singh Midha
report_errors.description: It's one banana Michael, what could it cost, ten dollars? If you didn't have adult onset diabetes, I wouldn't mind giving you a little sugar. There are very few intelligent, attractive and straight men in this town. Well, that certainly leaves me out. A-coodle-doodle-doo. A-coodle-doodle-doo. Ann certainly has a great deal of Mass. Sorry, some of my students are arguing the significance of the shankbone on the seder plate. But we do not - NOT wag our genitals at one another to make a point. I'm not a prostitute. Then I shall let you live!
